package.json.content:
{
  "name": "@inkathon/contracts",
  "type": "module",
  "private": true,
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "scripts": {
    "postinstall": "touch deployments/greeter/development.ts; true",
    "test": "./test-all.sh",
    "build": "./build-all.sh",
    "node": "substrate-contracts-node --dev --port 9944 --base-path ./.node-data",
    "script": "ts-node --cwd=scripts",
    "deploy": "pnpm run script deploy",
    "contracts-ui": "open https://contracts-ui.substrate.io/?rpc=ws://127.0.0.1:9944",
    "explorer-ui": "open https://polkadot.js.org/apps/#/explorer?rpc=ws://127.0.0.1:9944",
    "type-check": "tsc --pretty --noEmit",
    "lint": "prettier . --check && eslint",
    "lint:fix": "prettier . --write && eslint --fix",
    "lint:format": "prettier . --write",
    "eslint": "eslint . --ext .js,.ts"
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@polkadot/api": "^10.10.1",
    "@polkadot/api-contract": "^10.10.1",
    "@polkadot/keyring": "^12.5.1",
    "@polkadot/types": "^10.10.1",
    "@polkadot/util": "^12.5.1",
    "@polkadot/util-crypto": "^12.5.1",
    "@scio-labs/use-inkathon": "^0.1.0",
    "@types/node": "^18.18.5",
    "@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin": "^6.7.5",
    "@typescript-eslint/parser": "^6.7.5",
    "dotenv": "^16.3.1",
    "eslint": "^8.51.0",
    "eslint-config-prettier": "^9.0.0",
    "ts-node": "^10.9.1",
    "typescript": "^5.2.2"
  }
}

tsconfig.json.content:
{
  "ts-node": {
    "esm": true,
    "experimentalSpecifierResolution": "node"
  },
  "compilerOptions": {
    "module": "esnext",
    "moduleResolution": "node",
    "target": "esnext",
    "sourceMap": true,
    "outDir": "dist",
    "resolveJsonModule": true,
    "esModuleInterop": true,
    "skipLibCheck": true,
    "allowJs": true,
    "baseUrl": ".",
    "composite": true
  },
  "exclude": ["./*/target"],
  "include": ["./deployments/**/*.json", "./deployments/**/*.ts", "./scripts/**/*.ts"]
}
